  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">If a Sony Entertainment Network account holder plays a game that utilizes this feature, SCEA will log information about his or her system and game play to ensure that advertisements are being appropriately served to him or her and to track information about the advertisements displayed during his or her gaming session.</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

