  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">We may use log files to gather statistics about consumers' browsing habits and to assess overall website activity, including how many "hits" a particular web page is getting. These entries are generated anonymously, and enable us to track interest in specific promotions, troubleshoot technical concerns, and provide consumers with content that may be of interest to them.</evidenceContent>
